<div class="com-share" data-id="1329" data-title="《你好，本田牌飞机》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1329/medium/1329.jpg?1436640373" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1329.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
